SBADescriptor.Name: ControlUp Stress Settings calculator V2
SBADescriptor.Description: The ControlUp Stress Settings calculator enables you to use your own historical data to determine how to set your Stress thresholds in the real-time console. The calculator requires historical data exported from ControlUp Monitor of from ControlUp Insights. For full step-by-step instructions on preparing the data and using the calculator, please visit the following page: https://support.controlup.com/docs/stress-level-calculator-tool-v2
